msgstr " `OidcClient` 会发现令牌端点的URL是 `<a href=\"http://localhost:8180/auth/realms/quarkus/protocol/openid-connect/tokens\" class=\"bare\">http://localhost:8180/auth/realms/quarkus/protocol/openid-connect/tokens</a>` ."

