#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Refreshing access tokens"
msgstr "刷新访问令牌"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`OidcClientRequestReactiveFilter`, `OidcClientRequestFilter`, and `Tokens` producers refresh the current expired access token if a refresh token is available."
msgstr "如果有刷新令牌， `OidcClientRequestReactiveFilter` 、 `OidcClientRequestFilter` 和 `令牌` 生成器会刷新当前已过期的访问令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Additionally, you can use the `quarkus.oidc-client.refresh-token-time-skew` property for preemptive access token refresh to avoid sending nearly expired access tokens that might cause HTTP 401 errors."
msgstr "此外，你还可以使用 `quarkus.oidc-client.refresh-token-time-skew` 属性进行抢占式访问令牌刷新，以避免发送几乎过期的访问令牌而导致 HTTP 401 错误。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, if this property is set to `3S` and the access token will expire in less than 3 seconds, the token is refreshed automatically."
msgstr "例如，如果该属性设置为 `3S` ，且访问令牌将在 3 秒内过期，则会自动刷新令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, the OIDC client refreshes the token during the current request when it detects that the token has expired, or is nearly expired if the xref:#quarkus-oidc-client_quarkus-oidc-client-refresh-token-time-skew[refresh token time skew] is configured.\n"
"Performance-critical applications might want to avoid waiting for a possible token refresh during incoming requests and configure an asynchronous token refresh instead."
msgstr "默认情况下，当 OIDC 客户端检测到令牌已过期，或者如果配置了 xref:quarkus-oidc-client_quarkus-oidc-client-refresh-token-time-skew[刷新令牌时间偏移] ，令牌即将过期时，会在当前请求中 xref:quarkus-oidc-client_quarkus-oidc-client-refresh-token-time-skew[刷新令牌] 。对性能要求较高的应用程序可能希望避免在传入请求期间等待可能的令牌刷新，而是配置异步令牌刷新。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Check every minute whether the current access token is expired and must be refreshed."
msgstr "每分钟检查一次当前访问令牌是否过期，是否必须刷新。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the access token needs to be refreshed but no refresh token is available, an attempt is made to acquire a new token with a configured grant, such as `client_credentials`."
msgstr "如果访问令牌需要刷新，但没有可用的刷新令牌，则会尝试使用配置的授权（如 `client_credentials` ）获取新令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Some OpenID Connect providers do not return a refresh token in a `client_credentials` grant response.\n"
"For example, starting with Keycloak 12, a refresh token is not returned by default for `client_credentials`.\n"
"Providers might also restrict how many times a refresh token can be used."
msgstr "某些 OpenID Connect 提供商不会在 `客户证书` 授予响应中返回刷新令牌。例如，从 Keycloak 12 开始，默认情况下 `客户端凭据` 不会返回刷新令牌。提供商可能还会限制刷新令牌的使用次数。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Revoking access tokens"
msgstr "撤销访问令牌"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If your OpenID Connect provider, such as Keycloak, supports a token revocation endpoint, you can use `OidcClient#revokeAccessToken` to revoke the current access token.\n"
"The revocation endpoint URL is discovered alongside the token request URI or can be configured with `quarkus.oidc-client.revoke-path`."
msgstr "如果你的 OpenID Connect 提供商（如 Keycloak）支持令牌撤销端点，你可以使用 `OidcClient#revokeAccessToken` 撤销当前访问令牌。撤销端点 URL 与令牌请求 URI 一起被发现，也可以使用 `quarkus.oidc-client.revoke-path` 进行配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You might want to revoke the access token if a REST client call that uses this token fails with an HTTP `401` status code, or if the token has been used for a long time and you want to refresh it."
msgstr "如果使用该令牌的 REST 客户端调用失败并出现 HTTP `401` 状态代码，或者如果该令牌已使用很长时间，而你想刷新它，你可能会想撤销访问令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can do this by requesting a token refresh with a refresh token.\n"
"However, if the refresh token is unavailable, you can revoke the current access token first and then request a new access token."
msgstr "您可以使用刷新令牌请求刷新令牌。不过，如果刷新令牌不可用，可以先撤销当前的访问令牌，然后再申请一个新的访问令牌。"

