#. type: Title ==
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "RestClient JsonWebTokenRequestFilter"
msgstr "RestClient JsonWebTokenRequestFilter"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` is recommended if you work with Bearer JWT tokens whose claims, such as `issuer` and `audience`, can be modified and the updated tokens re-secured, for example, re-signed."
msgstr "如果您使用的是不记名 JWT 令牌，其声明（如 `发行者` 和 `受众` ）可以修改，更新后的令牌可以重新加密（如重新签名），则建议使用 `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It expects an injected `org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken` and therefore will not work with opaque tokens.\n"
"Also, if your OpenID Connect provider supports a Token Exchange protocol, it is recommended to use `AccessTokenRequestFilter` instead, because both JWT and opaque bearer tokens can be securely exchanged with `AccessTokenRequestFilter`."
msgstr "它需要注入 `org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken` ，因此无法使用不透明令牌。此外，如果您的 OpenID Connect 提供商支持令牌交换协议，建议使用 `AccessTokenRequestFilter` 代替，因为 JWT 和不透明承载令牌都可以通过 `AccessTokenRequestFilter` 安全交换。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` makes it easy for `Service A` implementations to update the injected `org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken` with the new `issuer` and `audience` claim values and secure the updated token again with a new signature.\n"
"The only difficult step is ensuring that `Service A` has a signing key, which should be provisioned from a secure file system or remote secure storage such as Vault."
msgstr "`JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` 可让 `服务 A` 实现轻松地使用新的 `签发人` 和 `受众` 声明值更新注入的 `org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken` ，并使用新签名再次保护更新后的令牌。唯一困难的步骤是确保 `服务 A` 拥有签名密钥，该密钥应从安全文件系统或远程安全存储（如 Vault）中调配。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can selectively register `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` by using either `io.quarkus.oidc.token.propagation.JsonWebToken` or `org.eclipse.microprofile.rest.client.annotation.RegisterProvider`, for example:"
msgstr "你可以通过使用 `io.quarkus.oidc.token.propagation.JsonWebToken` 或 `org.eclipse.microprofile.rest.client.annotation.RegisterProvider` ，有选择地注册 `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` ，例如。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Alternatively, `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` can be registered automatically with all MicroProfile REST or Jakarta REST clients if both the `quarkus.resteasy-client-oidc-token-propagation.register-filter` and `quarkus.resteasy-client-oidc-token-propagation.json-web-token` properties are set to `true`."
msgstr "另外，如果 `quarkus.resteasy-client-oidc-token-propagation.register-filter` 和 `quarkus.resteasy-client-oidc-token-propagation.json-web-token` 属性都设置为 `true` ， `JsonWebTokenRequestFilter` 可以在所有 MicroProfile REST 或 Jakarta REST 客户端自动注册。"

#. type: Title ===
